    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Craft Spell Engine, caster level 4th.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When recharging a spell engine, you may spend a number of spell points not exceeding half your caster level, restoring an equal number of spell points to the spell engine.</p>\n<p>You may not exceed the spell engine&#8217;s maximum charges this way. You may recharge a spell engine more than once a day with this ability, but the total transferred spell points cannot exceed half your caster level. Additionally, you may count your caster level as 4 higher when determining what spell engines you can recharge.</p>\n",
